snippet.title: HeroWarz Official - The Prologue
snippet.description:
Year 2016, according to myth, the old world was taken by the seas. 
Everything that existed then was submerged in water.

Check out our Official Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/HeroWarzGlobal/
